{"text": "WOW! So much fun! The game tells so many stories through a rather simple, and hilarious game-play loop where you build a party and watch it get destroyed by 'the horror, the horror' of the darkest dungeon. You will laugh and have a ball as your party have heart-attacks, attack and blame each other and accumulate numerous mental illnesses. After a mission they will rest up for a while, drinking themselves to death, cavorting with hookers, preying to God or being treated in a mental asylum. The art style is great. The music and voice work is great. Highly recommended.", "appid": "262060", "steamid": "profiles/76561198009205423", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1593172800.0}
