{"text": "A fun game with lots of replay value. You'll spend hours unlocking all the characters, traits, items, and super abilities. Then you can create custom characters made out of everything you unlocked. The game has you travel through a city eventually reaching the Mayor's location and then you have multiple ways to proceed. I just played through as the zombie character. I was supposed to kill and zombify everyone. Instead I was elected into the position of mayor by the voters I had won over when traveling through the city. This required saving up a lot of money from like selling bats and knives and using the money to remove traits that made my zombie unable to speak and one that made people either flee in terror or attack me when seeing me. So I was a friendly zombie. Though of course killing and zombifying everyone would have been the easier option. This game is a lot of fun. There's some grind but you do it just by playing the game. Unlocking traits and items require chicken nuggets which you get my leveling up as you travel through the levels. You just do a run through the city and you get several nuggets just by playing. I highly recommend this game.", "appid": "512900", "steamid": "profiles/76561198008929643", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1562673600.0}
