{"text": "Distraint is a game that tells a story about how greed destroys the soul of its main character, Price. It is a short yet terrifying look at how the guilt and emotions a person may feel from hurting others for their own gain cannot be erased or suppressed. No matter the lip service a person might give to others to compensate for taking advantage of them, the guilt of their conscience will chase them down and kill them. As the scenarios in Distraint show, those most likely to be abused are poor, elderly, or vulnerable in some way. Ultimately, \"what goes around comes around.\" A nice little story with a lesson on morality, set in uniquely terrifying environments.", "appid": "395170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198001782126", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578744000.0}
