{"text": "I absolutely adore this game. Every round is a fresh experience, you never know what the outcome will be, nothing is ever set in stone. Some rounds feel like a thrilling game of hide and seek, others are an all out war. The learning curve is somewhat steep, and rather unforgiving since you only have one life per round. But eventually you learn, and you start to win, and the satisfaction that comes from looking back at where you started, to where you are now, is simply immesurable. But let's get something straight right now. If you are interested in this game. DO NOT BUY THE STARTER EDITION. BUY AT LEAST THE STANDARD EDITION. The Starter Edition is cheaper to buy, but the grind to unlock new operators is much higher, so it's really not worth it.", "appid": "359550", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042872523", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1534075200.0}
