{"text": "Just like the Devs previous work, this sweet and honest short story tells of love and romance and the potential trails that come with them. The music is very soothing and calming, to a point that it matches the atmospheric art and sound design.  Adding to the fact that a lot of small details were put into consideration such as the minimalist approach to the design and the simple UI that is pleasing to the eye, it nails that part pretty decently. Would like more buttons like a fast forward or an auto scroller for text since this is a Visual Novel but if that is the most I can critic, then you can guess that the experience, short as it may be, was really neat and positive! :D", "appid": "1297160", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045706005", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "12", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1590062400.0}
