{"text": "Disclaimer: I received this pack as a donation from a viewer, I was planning to buy this later that month. First of all, the developers are amazing. They were always there to answer questions in their discord and helped me set it up for my twitch streams and connect the loyalty currency from streamlabs. As of June 8, 2019 there are 110 workshop character packs made by players. There are also a few premade packs to use inside of Stream Avatars. It is pretty easy to make recolors for characters you download.  Important links: Stream Avatars example commands list. Twitch extension: Stream Avatars discord: Stream Avatars setup help: Feel free to comment on review and add me if you would like to see how stream avatars looks during a stream:", "appid": "665300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198162234242", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1559995200.0}
{"text": "Easily one of the best games I've ever purchased.  The story is so well written and emotional, it'll make you laugh and cry. The characters are incredible along with their character development and I adore the personalities they all have. They do a great job making you care about them. The atmosphere is dark and creepy and then other times it's bright and beautiful. The gameplay is also a lot of fun from the crafting, to the stealth, to all the weapons and elixirs. I enjoyed it all. And the soundtrack is so mesmerizing.  This masterpiece is also perfect for screenshot lovers like myself with the beautiful aesthetic it has and the photo mode. It has so many beautiful places to take pictures of. This game is truly something special and it deserves all the love. 10/10 â™¡", "appid": "752590", "steamid": "profiles/76561198316928182", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "31", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1576756800.0}
