{"text": "In this game you act as a leader to a clan of people who have been forced to migrate to a new region.  It's a very unique kind of strategy game where you have to learn and use the traditional ways of your people in order to survive and prosper, while also overcoming the cultural challenges of getting your people to adopt a new way of life.   I highly recommend this game.  It has many positive qualities: it's extremely well written and unlike any other game out there (except for King of Dragon Pass, the game's predecessor).  It's greatest merit is the vividly realized game world, which I consider a real wonder among video games.", "appid": "881420", "steamid": "profiles/76561197992051132", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "7", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1586174400.0}
