{"text": "Cute little witches have more than one trick up their sleeve. In this game, you will have to give them a hand to make more and more magic potions in a given time. Alone or with friends, the only detail that is important is to have a good memory. Abracadabrew is a game where you will have to create magic potions. For this, it will be necessary to follow the different recipes to the letter. But the only problem is that the ingredients are hidden all over the room. We will therefore have to dig, to find the ingredients we need. Everything goes there, from the paw of a purple frog, to the orange mandrake. Once we have been able to find the hiding places, it will be worth memorizing them, in order to be able to find them very quickly, during the making. Abracadabrew can be played alone or with up to four players. Personally, we enjoyed it more than alone. Because firstly, we can share the tasks. And second, it's clearly more fun. Especially since alone or with others, the difficulty of the recipes does not change, which makes the solo challenge more complicated. The game has a cute art direction. We have the right to a very childish universe, with colorful decorations. And very charming witches. The music enchants us as much as the potions of our little witches. It is varied. And change, depending on the room you are in. Of course, it is true that we are so focused, that we run so everywhere, and we shout at each other. That we no longer really pay attention. To conclude, Abracadabrew is much more fun when you are lucky enough to be able to play it with others. Even with children. So yes obviously, it will be necessary to start again a hundred times before achieving all the objectives. But we have fun so easily, that we repeat the experience again and again.", "appid": "1233250", "steamid": "profiles/76561198077624633", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1602763200.0}
