{"text": "This game unlike many others nowadays is actually really fun to play. Its feels like a refreshed version of Rebellion's \"Zombie Army Trilogy\" game combined with puzzles like in tomb raider.  A 1930's adventure game taking place in Egypt, seeking treasure and solving puzzles all while you battle your way through hoards of dead mummies and interesting bosses. The level design and map detail in this game is outstanding. The gameplay is fun and satisfying, the puzzles are cute, the guns, customization and gamemodes are also pretty decent.  Overall this a casual game but an exceptionally fun one to play. A must play in coop with friends. The game is a bit pricey so that might be the biggest reason affecting your decision to buy.. In my opinion, if your looking for something new and actually fun to play among the heap of questionable games out there right now, I reccomend picking this up.  Bravo! 8/10", "appid": "312670", "steamid": "profiles/76561197993310177", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "41", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1535457600.0}
