{"text": "I've been playing this games for years now and despite some balance issues wich get fixed here and there the game is just great !  It's an action filled 2D Moba where the team effort and strategy gets you the win, you can only play as a team of 3 people and against a team of 3 but the many maps, characters and playstyles each of them can have makes each team and match unique !  The game has only one large flaw... there's no one playing it !  The devs had to choose between a bad matchmaking (you get to play against way better player then you because no one else with your level is playing at the moment) or make you wait up to 6 minutes to launch the game... I don't care about waiting because I get to do a lot of stuff I wouldn't be doing if there was no restriction but many people do care about that and stop playing because of this issue... People leave because of this matchmaking but there can not be any good matchmaking if no one is playing ! It's a loophole the game has been struggling in since years !  The game is free so please do me a favor, if you like the game just talk about it to friends so we get more players to play !", "appid": "204300", "steamid": "profiles/76561198188732518", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "3", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1530532800.0}
