{"text": "This game does not only incorporate zombie killing action, it allows the players to create a survival group just like the walking dead. If you are in love with the Walking Dead TV series, this game is for you! It has the ability to not only go out and scout for supplies for your home base but it also has a drama system inside and outside your home. The home is used for safety so save and quit and also to heal up and repair weapons. Melee weapons is the key to the survival of the game. The game has a sound system, zombies can see you but it is very rare and difficult, the sound is what drives them crazy and makes them run straight at you. I find for a early access game, this game has rarely any glitches but the screen is a little wobbly but you will adjust to it after awhile. Day Z and War Z are just no compare to this game. If you really want to experience a true zombie apocalypse this game has it all!", "appid": "241540", "steamid": "profiles/76561198045279755", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1380628800.0}
