{"text": "I received the game for free thanks to the Humble Bundle Play Outlast is a game full of blood, violence and fear in the game he played for a journalist who wanted to reject the law of the abandoned Psichiatria but did not know that there were things that marked him for life. The game contains RPG elements of classical Horror, such as collecting documents, exploring the environment, and collecting the flashlight. It is true that the game has beautiful and breathtaking graphics with places with which man also freezes but such a player does not fear horror so do not expect anything from it because I was not afraid at all. The game is optimized with excellent texture, sound effects and NPC characters, and the Camera of the Hero is excellently crafted and can be seen from your character but forgot to give the mirror the heads and NPC reflections. PROS + Graphics + A breathtaking environment + Blood and other effects are processed in detail + The water is processed in detail and contains Physx (when water flows through it) + true horror atmosphere + Night vision is extremely effective + Camera is processed in detail + Models and textures are nice and done in high resolution to praise the Creators + beautiful sound effects and NPC sounds and spooky sounds + the story and its end   CONS - Short but if you enjoy the game, it will last for 7,5 hours, which is the perfect length of the FPS shooter. - Smoother landscaping GAME 7/10", "appid": "238320", "steamid": "profiles/76561198335973146", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "5", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1506772800.0}
