{"text": "HotLead is an unpolished game in every sense of the word.   The game mechanics  like jumping, cover system are out of whack and not even a mouse sensitivity option.  You look like an erect robo-penis when you jump in this game.  The graphics are quite nice though but the rest of the game like gameplay, sound and story is just pure garbage. Avoid at all cost.   It's a freaking Doughnut as in Do Not Buy unless it's free ofcourse then by all means grab it for the trading cards and earn a few cents from it.", "appid": "416170", "steamid": "profiles/76561198296798593", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "27", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1463572800.0}
