{"text": "I really like this game. It should be a 10/10 It hurts to give it a thumb down. But with some fixes, it will be great!  Why must it be THAT FRUSTRATING? With those random generated trails, it will never get boring, true. But at the other hand it makes it less enjoyable. You can't memorize anything, so you can't optimize your track and find your preferred path. You must slow down your run to not loose health, And you need a lot of health for end bosses.  Then those random generated \"additional goals\" sometimes do not fit the generated trail and can not be achieved unless you loose some health. The end bosses are very hard to complete and the way to get there is boring, frustrating and too time consuming.  - Please give me more options in the way of difficulty settings (easy, hard, very hard etc). Lower difficulty = less reputation, but easier trails. Higher difficulty = more reputation, cool item drops etc. - Please fix the stunts so they are manageable. Some at the mountain map are unpassable. Some cant be completed at lower speed (and you dont know you need speed, because its a random obstacle placement). - Please fix those obstacle where you just fly into air and can not land properly, because its too high.  - Please fix the end bosses. They sometimes cant be completed at lower speed from last checkpoint (eg. Pyramid 360)  - Please add a button to quickly restart a session. If I fail at the first run, i really want to restart the whole session and do not prefer to lower my health to death first (takes me 1 min of stupid falling off my bike)... - Please give me some teammembers that we can choose from at the start of the session and unlocking better ones while playing.  - Where can we train the map \"Cunstruction area\"? Its freaking insane.  - When it's night, why is it not changing to daylight again? Once night, always night?  Thanks developers to consider some of those fixes. Greetings", "appid": "681280", "steamid": "profiles/76561197970587998", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1579348800.0}
