{"text": "Pro :  _ Great graphics, special effects and sound environnement. _ Boss battles are pretty cool. That's all.  Cons :  _This game is slow, which make the gameplay terrible :  __ Your character is too slow. The \"light\" weight config in this game is the \"medium\" one in DS. You will fatroll a lot with the wrong equipement and config. So you will use shortcut to switch between armors and weapons while a combat to have something \"fair\" at the right moment. Amazing experience. __ On a controller, button registration are too slow. Be ready to die or take stupid damage cos the game didn't registered to dodge/parry/run at the right moment. Sometimes, it is just the mob which are broken because of bad coding. __ The camera is too slow, even with the higher sensibility and/or locked on an ennemy. Plus, the bad automatic view is horribly managed. It will make you killed against walls or in corridor because the camera will automatically choose a wrong angle where you will see nothing but a wall texture. Then, you ll lose time to center the camera on the combat. Amazing experience.   _ Magic. Spells are simply OP. Almost at the third of the game, when you ll start to have a decent build, you will be able to face any situation with the strenght of thousands suns. Big damage, big range, pretty fast reload. Magic items are strong too. For example, one of them accelerate the mana regeneration and an other one give you a nice health regeneration. Lot of power. The thing is without magic or combat skills you can't do nothing, but if you mix both, you will be a semi-god. In endgame, you can rule only by magic effortlessly. _ No map, no second quest reminder. The level design is so poor than everything have the same taste. Except if you have good sense heading, you ll forget where things are. The big problem is that you need to come back a lot of time on already visited places for many reasons. You d better draw or take screenshot with notifications. _ Except bosses, combat is generic. Almost every mob have 2 kind of totally breakable attacks. Once you are used with (10 seconds, no more), you ll start rolling on ennemies because it is a really simple AI with really simple moves. I repeat, only the camera and slow gameplay will kill you. _ Bad key mapping, it is the same button to jump and roll. Prepare to roll in pits and jump in ennemy's attacks. To sum up, this game is only for the eyes and the ears, not much.", "appid": "265300", "steamid": "profiles/76561197998411882", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "3", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1508846400.0}
