{"text": "The game has sadly become excedingly pay to win.  Unique and well constructed robots pretty much no longer exist, almost every bot you will see will be a variation on whatever the current meta is.  The game also penalizes your standing in the leagues and thus your chances of getting better items, which are required to play in higher leagues, by rating your performance entirely on whether you win or lose, get matched with crappy players over and over and you can drop entire ranks and theres nothing you can do about it. The loot system is one of the worst systems I've ever seen outside of iphone games where your forced to watch advertisements. Opening crates often taunts you with high powered items you cant have unless you pay for premium, and the only way to build a specific item is to sell your existing stuff for insignificant amounts of ingame currency. There is a massive lack of balance between the power and rarity of items. If a player refuses to pay money, they are forced into an endless pvp grind where their opponents will oftentimes have higher tier equipment that will win in nearly every fight.", "appid": "301520", "steamid": "profiles/76561198139595094", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": true, "tstamp_created": 1492430400.0}
