uantity over quality and USA is the opposite. But I haven't seen quality win EVER it's always spam out units unless you want a tank. Nothing else. Also out of the few games I've played ONLY ONE I had a good teammate. I havint played much because as mentioned before the servers are the worst thing ever. Speaking of servers, the lobby list is broken as â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥, you see something you like, you try and click on it, suddenly 2 new games pop up/disappear and now you're in some random Russian server. It bounces around so â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥â™¥ much that it might as well be a minigame trying to join a lobby. Also since the maps are very very unbalanced, the king of the hill game mode is the worst thing ever, instead of 2 people barely having enough terrain to fight over, you have FOUR. The game is only filled with tryhards who payed for the game so good luck not losing if you're a noob.", "appid": "302670", "steamid": "profiles/76561198079749040", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "10", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1525176000.0}
