{"text": "An absolutely garbage game... The match-3 sections are too numerous and often tedious, and you'll either spend hours on a puzzle before realizing the game stuck its pieces in a position where they can't be moved at all, or you'll just realize it's faster to activate a speed hack and skip everything to death. The hidden object scenes are unimaginative, the other puzzles are done to death and offer zero challenge, except in patience, because the animations are horribly slow. The story is ridiculous and terribly written. The ending doesn't even bother to do more than show two sentences of text. The graphics are subpar for a hidden object game. Possibly the worst game I've finished in a year. I don't know why I finished it, actually. I kept thinking, \"you know it's not going to end on a good note, don't you?\"... And I was right. To the bin!", "appid": "1002280", "steamid": "profiles/76561198081340622", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "4", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1591272000.0}
