{"text": "This is a game with a message, and the message is BEWARE!. This is not a game for playing -- this is a game for uninstalling and avoiding. This game is only for those keen on regurgitation. I think â€“ no, Iâ€™m positive - that this is the most unattractive game I have ever played in my entire life. You know, in the short time I played this, this game demonstrated every loathsome characteristic of bad game design and even discovered a few new ones. It is visually repulsive, and intellectually retarded. Charging money for this is morally reprehensible, vulgar, insensitive, selfish, and stupid. The game has no purpose, a lousy sense of functionality and is broken in every sense of the word. I played Busby 3D, one of the worst platformers ever made, CortexGear:AngryDroids makes Busby 3D better, more enjoyable by just existing and lowering the bar.", "appid": "375620", "steamid": "profiles/76561197964178108", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "20", "votes_funny": "6", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1455451200.0}
