{"text": "I cannot recommend Dead by Daylight at all. First of all, the game is extremely unbalanced. Second, the game is a p2w, every DLC killer down to 1-2 (including Pyramid Head) are OPs can teleport or even turn off their terror radius. Thirdly, most players are small children who should not play this game (you can only see what they write in the text fields after each game, most of them are toxic) or they are adults who behave like 12 year olds. The developers give me the impression that they are not working on any of these problems and are simply using season passes and co. want to make easy money.", "appid": "381210", "steamid": "profiles/76561198120988656", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1592568000.0}
