{"text": "For a game that's been in development this long with the amount of money they've made it's really really rough around the edges, or as my friend calls it \"clunky\". It looks really pretty but constantly run into weird mechanics that are half-assed and unpolished. As well for as much time spent on the in-game models it seems very little time was spent with the UI and UX, especially the map -- something that seems to be common with MMO WWII Sim cash grabs of it's time like Hell Let Loose. Maybe try it again in a year see if it's improved.", "appid": "736220", "steamid": "profiles/76561197962624598", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "2", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1587816000.0}
