{"text": "Well, no. And i really wanted to like this game!:-/ Been following news since it was announced, been disapointed during beta and confirmed my impressions during free weekend. The idea of the game is great, bunch of mercenaries clearing Bolivia out of drug cartels while unlocking tons and tons of stuff, like weapon accessories and various cosmetics.  Game runs great given my setup is quite trash and even gtx750ti is able to handle medium/high details while very rarely going under 40fps if you are not insisting on very high resolution.  Shooting feels great, there is huge variety of weapons and custom parts, sure, its not Tarkov, bud its still great when it comes to \"gun porn\" element. AI is decent enought, both enemy and your squadies.  Now you probably ask why thumbs down?! .... couse DRIVING anything feels like crap! I never experienced that bad driving in game, and my gaming career started more than 30yrs ago in 8bit era, so i have seen a lot of bad driving. But really, what Wildlands is offering us is so bad that i just can not enjoy the game even i love everything else about the game.  Tought OK, i will just use helicopter to move my team around, and you know what? It sux as well, even its not that bad as wheeled vehicles, but it still, sux pretty hard.  Sorry Wildlands, wanted to love you, but found out i cant:-/", "appid": "460930", "steamid": "profiles/76561198042623305", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "1", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1523707200.0}
{"text": "The cutscenes look like the characters are made out of clay and the cutscenes voice acting sucks. The voices WITH the cutscnes are out of sync and the gameplay is confusing witth so many combinations. It's not even worth the 50% I paid and I'm getting a refund. I tried to give this game a chance and it isn't worth it sadly. Maybe with some more updates? I can't even score it because i had to refund it after 20 minutes.", "appid": "338390", "steamid": "profiles/76561198189818942", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "9", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1478001600.0}
